It's World Vegan Day! @marianilastockholm is 100% Vegan & Cruelty Free and a strong believer of keeping animals apart from human vanity. They are fundraising for the endangered beluga whales and more specifically for Little Grey & Little White living in the world's first @belugawhalesanctuary. The sanctuary has made it possible for them to be released into the open sea, free from a life in captivity. By using the code BELUGA at marianila.com, you will receive a 20% discount and your full purchase of USD will go directly to support Little Grey & Little White. Thank you @marianilastockholm @belugawhalesanctuary @tpw_foundation #ad #marianila #ichoosefriendly #worldveganday
